libdatetime-locale-perl (1:0.45-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
    + Breaks libdatetime-format-strptime-perl (< 1.2000)
  * Add lintian override for spelling-error-in-manpage: "nam" is used as an
    abbreviation for the German word "nachmittags".
  * debian/copyright: Update years of copyright, minor changes for DEP 5.
  * Use source format 3.0 (quilt).
  * Add myself to Uploaders.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 3.8.4.

